message.body: Oh sorry just want to see how your week is going
I'm doing all right. Went out a bit for the weekend. How's it going over there?
Oh that's awesome. How's the weather when you're out? I just began a new term for summer
It was good. Kinda hot, but it's summer. Are you done all of your coops?
Yeah summer is nice. At least it wasn't raining. I'm done! Just school now
